---
title: Mediterranean Turkey Burgers with Sweet Potatoes
description: The noble burger, a thing of such delicious, dribble-down-your-chin simplicity, can be re-invented time and time again to create the most divine dinnertime results. For this incarnation, we've put a Greek twist on it with ground turkey and feta cheese!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-de-dinde-facon-mediterraneenne-dd443831.jpg
